Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:23.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:30.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:54.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:57.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:06.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:16.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:21.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜欢着紧张的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:23.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}兴奋起来走向更广阔的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:30.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只专注于眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谁都无法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}连同那份泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部开始闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:54.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此将宿于手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:57.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}尽情挥扬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果断地  径直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向着明天全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:06.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在转瞬即逝之间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}实现那梦中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}无论它多么虚幻和遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:16.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和仅属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:21.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹剑节奏响彻永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是勇次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小珠人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠在家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我明天要休假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把竹剑拿回来打算调养一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家怎么都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为为了帮宫崎同学做特训
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演看得怎么样  玩得尽兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小珠她很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然是头一次见  很难得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.69,0:00:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不同于常日的青春性质的展开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为勇次君就是勇次君嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…你们说什么啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这点并不让我讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:34.03,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第21话\N川添珠姬和铃木凛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德  你为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒你  我再一次从地狱回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始延长战吧！布雷巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德  复活了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  然后这时候爆炸  呯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈尔登场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈尔  参上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧场版的新角色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是支持施奈德的谜之女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身份谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧中嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔那里没有女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过藤村先生的表演比女性更女性化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前暂时撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说的话就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴！下会见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次  就要和你结束这场比赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨亮你那身铠甲给我等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  两位继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底  打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你看来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴之流  就请你干脆地把他做掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那故事不就大变样了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐一说到施奈德  就整个变了一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她原来也会那样笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴巾我放这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  比小珠大一岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看起来还是比较像大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  铃木凛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家都叫她小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  往那一站就有种大小姐气质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和小珠处好就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子还是太小孩子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我想可能差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看小姐那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还真是了不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…床和地铺  你要睡哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡地铺就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在家也这样睡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢布雷巴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢他哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的使者  又厉害  还很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么面对敌人都不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…铃木小姐你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我凛就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛你  喜欢施…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VHD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点睡吧  明天还要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  明天要几点起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是7点出场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以6点出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以5点起床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5点是吧  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和第39话的「泪水中的东西友情」中\N大阪大爆炸中使用的倒计时钟一样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布雷巴阻止的那个炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那里得到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么特有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在贩卖网站上看到了相同式样的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止这个定式炸弹的场面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我心中的名场面排名中名列第三呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那一和二是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是施奈德初次登场是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二是出现必杀施奈台风的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是施奈德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你心中的名场面又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从10位开始是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超燃的啊  那个武道馆决战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那话里面  我非常喜欢在得知敌人就是教剑道的爷爷的时候红色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握着剑的手这样不停地颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那时候  施奈德和布雷巴第一次合作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是施奈德不出手相助的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴就要在那里完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得这里应该会有什么办法解决
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不会输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为布雷巴是正义的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添  看来你还没注意到布雷巴的弱点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且刚才你说得一副好像布雷巴阻止爆炸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上是施奈德阻止的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事  是布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剑战队BLADE BRAVER！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红还是白？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断哪条线才能停止爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没黄色的话就应该是白色了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是红色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的占卜是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…到底是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是红色  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢才
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色代表末路  终焉的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑士的话  就砍红色！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLADE BRAVE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CUTTING END
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  不是布雷巴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  因为有施奈德的指引才成功的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上不还是施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算布雷巴一个人也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这后面的40话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈台风！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别搞错了  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了她而战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了祝福！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少磨蹭了！快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  没有施奈德的话  结婚典礼就没法开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么我的敌人会救助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能亲手打倒你们的  只有我而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个…了断吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是令人感动的画面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施…施奈德他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来处得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的门「唰」地打开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓住的人们逃出来后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了阻止他们竹剑插入地面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈尔登场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添  吃糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点  因为是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事的话就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛也是演员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点戏份  只是个逃跑的女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是藤村的错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又旧又锈的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那找谁替代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人穿得了施奈戈尔的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要删镜头来混过关么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也要有个限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大  这不行啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要破坏孩子的梦想啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我还行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别硬撑了  藤村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆给别的事务所打电话找个谁来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈尔的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部都记在脑子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台词会在拍好之后再加进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要站着就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐也比较敏捷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之别太勉强自己啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈尔把想要逃走的众人赶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了示众正准备用竹剑攻击一个女学生的时候  布雷巴登场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小姐演施奈戈尔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女学生不就没了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就说不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里要有个女孩子就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按照预定的行动就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的问题大家会处理好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救～命～啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快往外跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都将要成为Death Armour复活用的能量源！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐很入戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗的家伙都将成为竹剑下的尸骸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啊  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该怎么做来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈戈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么名堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重拍！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都给我先去冷静下头脑！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暂停一会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暂停一会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂停一会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊  导演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那两个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟  是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自做一些剧本里没有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我没能在那里停止继续演下去的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看到你  总感觉到心里有什么东西不能平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到凛你就不由自主的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  没有的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更强一些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你是布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  布雷巴从来就没有败过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而施奈德在最后的那几场里好几次都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说布雷巴赢不过施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可拜托你们了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抢了布雷巴出场的镜头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次拍摄开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难以置信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们部的成员会在休息日自发的出勤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就表示大家都很有干劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为部长你应该感到高兴才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到小珠的加入能一下带来这么大的变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不光是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你拼命努力的去支撑着这个部也很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得大家也不会集中在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家也不会像现在这样相识了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你是个很了不起的家伙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算那样奉承我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得不到任何好处啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是想说这些话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…这种空气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪…纪梨乃  快拿空气清新剂来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我是害虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢不言败的你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你那种鼓励对我是很强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫玛莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能熟练使用二刀流  可见她在体力上非常了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学锻炼一下绝对没有坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是玛莉是凯莉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…好直接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫我来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可以我休息日锻炼的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我到今天之前都没见到你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你在奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:19:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我会比你奔跑的更多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间的差距不会缩短
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等于呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要赢我是没可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学现在就像变了一个人一样在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会打败你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过不了多久…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我就在想一定有那种可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也会在关东大会出场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东大会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要战  不如就在公开的场合一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Adios{\r}\N再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…话说这不是墨西哥人说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自主练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你是最认真的一个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我昨天玩了一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也想确认一下竹剑的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去  礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研修…是去了冲绳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…因为没时间了  所以就在车站附近买的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在这段时间有发生什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到新朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但搞不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该叫「对手」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:21:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪个学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有进剑道部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…在关东大会上我们能见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候…我们再继续今天的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:22.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:27.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
