Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:35.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:40.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:48.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:22.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:27.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:34.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:55.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:23:02.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:10.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:17.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:20.44,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.73,0:23:25.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:32.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:35.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:40.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:48.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我出演电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明年要上映的布雷巴剧场版
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.62,0:24:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演的角色是女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台词是「救～命～啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定要去看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前预定还有送布雷巴的扇子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.81,0:24:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能在电影院和我握手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前  下一集的BAMBOO BLADE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「败者与胜者」也请一定要看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
